  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构的示意图，用于下周的协议讲解。最前面应该是源端口和目的端口，各占16位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，0到15位是源端口，16到31位是目的端口。接下来应该是序列号吧？我记得TCP是32位的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequence Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，32到63位是序列号，然后64到95位是确认号。这两个都是32位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，序列号和确认号都加上了。接下来是数据偏移和保留位，然后到标志位部分了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "标志位那里要注意，URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN这六个标志各占1位，从106位排到111位。然后112到127位是窗口大小。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "标志位和窗口都画好了。后面应该是校验和、紧急指针，然后有个选项和填充的字段对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "Options and Padding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，紧急指针是144到159位，但选项和填充的范围应该是160到191位，不是192开始。192到255位才是真正的数据部分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "Options and Padding",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，修正过来了。160-191位是选项和填充，192-255位是数据。这样整个TCP报文结构就完整了，标题用\"TCP Packet Structure\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options and Padding",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这个标题很清晰。整体结构没问题了，感谢！",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TCP Packet Structure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
